milestones.description: Viv Richards has become the top scorer for WI in ODIs with 328 runs, going past Alvin Kallicharran's 313
Clive Lloyd has broken the record for most sixes (5) in ODIs for WI, going past Greenidge's 4
Holder has broken the record for most catches (6) in ODIs for WI, going past Clive Lloyd's 5
Andy Roberts has become the top wicket-taker for WI in ODIs with 17 wickets, going past Julien's 14
Fredericks has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (10) for WI, going past Holder
Derek Randall and Robin Jackman's 55-run partnership is the highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 48 between Dayle Hadlee and McKechnie
Derek Randall and Robin Jackman's 55-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 35 between Geoff Arnold and Fletcher
Clive Lloyd and Viv Richards's 68-run partnership is WI's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 50 between Rohan Kanhai and Clive Lloyd
Viv Richards and Holding's 39-run partnership is WI's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 24 between Deryck Murray and Julien
